<h3 id="government">government</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>Therefore, we examine whether return predictability and portfolio performance are compromised for SOEs 
where government signaling plays such a prominent role.</p>

  <p>Given that China has been experiencing a highly dynamic development through a series of structural breaks, implementing various 
financial reforms, and expanding its capital marketsâ€™ openness, we conjecture that highly 
fiexible methods are required to account for the Chinese marketâ€™s specificity.</p>

